774,"uid":171157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"好嬲下喎打咁大篇字<br />\n利申tldr"},{"pid":"86e07f53b39f8694b159170de7d33965554a7f9a","tid":869774,"uid":195623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"好幼稚"},{"pid":"39b4d9a85742fd5eda201cc73df2753d6eac319d","tid":869774,"uid":171277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬你都話e d係比較social既人<br />\n<br />\n即係其實比起你，其他人更喜歡佢"},{"pid":"53447506c1e470e60cb6825dbffce3554f69b229","tid":869774,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"39b4d9a85742fd5eda201cc73df2753d6eac319d","tid":869774,"uid":171277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大佬你都話e d係比較social既人<br />\n<br />\n即係其實比起你，其他人更喜歡佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"照我睇 應該係樓主因愛成恨"},{"pid":"b0bb13239b28e8b8f286cbf7cab9b46a9583dd69","tid":869774,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"呢啲叫小人 八婆 敬而遠之"},{"pid":"563d7047f9ee956a05403ee5db7a3b0f658c932c","tid":869774,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"你練大隻啲佢見到你就要收皮啦"}]}